	    <h2> Using the Mammouth MP2 super computer: steps to follow </h2>
	    
        <p>
          To get a working account on Sherbrooke's Mammouth MP2 super computer, you must go through the
          following steps. Be warned that your account is to be used only during the course's trimester
          and only as part of the assignments/project of this course.
        </p>

	    <ul>
          <li> Create account on Compute Canada platform by computing online form: <a href="https://ccdb.computecanada.ca/security/accept_aup">https://ccdb.computecanada.ca/security/accept_aup</a>
          <li> 
	    </ul>

	    <p>
	      If you ever need assistance with these steps, post a question on the 
	      <a href="https://groups.google.com/forum/?fromgroups#!forum/ift-725-a2012">discussion forum</a>!
	    </p>

	      
